txt.en: 'Are you looking to be welcomed into the inner circle of the Théodred's Riders? I can help you with that and make you a \qKindred\q of Théodred's Riders.\n\n'If this sounds good to you, speak to me again!'
'Alright, soon you will be Kindred of the Théodred's Riders. Ready?'
By completing this quest, you will be considered Kindred of Théodred's Riders.
